title: As season nears end, Rodney Howard may be finding his form -  The Atlanta Journal Constitution
content: As season nears end, Rodney Howard may be finding his form   The Atlanta Journal Constitution
description: In the final quarter of the season, two of Georgia Tech’s season-long quests may have been achieved. Coach Josh Pastner’s desire for production out of the post and a consistent third scorer may have been met in the form of center Rodney Howard.
